# 1) Dates: dd/mm/yyyy and dd.mm.yyyy and yyyy-mm-dd (different separators)
today 11/01/2026 and also 11.01.26 and iso 2026-01-11

# 2) Times: 00:00 | 00:00:00 | 00:00:00.0000 (digits vs separators vs subsep)
start 09:30 end 11:00
with seconds 12:34:56
with fractional 12:34:56.0000 and also 23:59:59.9 and 00:00:00.123456

# 3) Tick-boxes: [X] [-] [O] [ ] (each symbol its own color) + brackets
[X] done item
[-] paused item
[O] optional item
[ ] open item

# 4) Combo: checkbox + text + EOL ">" (this should override normal checkbox + gt)
[X] publish daily report to acta diurna >
[ ] write new post draft about domains and kingdoms >

# 5) EOL greater-than alone
this line ends with a gt >
this one has spaces before it      >

# 6) Pipes are individual contexts (each | should pop)
alpha | beta | gamma | delta

# 7) XML/HTML-like tags
<tag>
<foo-bar>
<todo>  # lowercase tag name; should still match tag rule
<Todo>  # IMPORTANT: context clash: this should be tag, not reserved keyword

# 8) Tag with colon-value form (<> / name / : / value)
<priority : high>
<track : stocks>
<topic : bioinformatics>

# 9) Curly int form: {00}, {123}, {0009}
batch {00} retry {12} seed {0009} take {123456}

# 10) Bracket pair contexts (content inside gets special scope)
square [any text here 123 !?] end
angle <any text here 456 @#$> end
curly {any text here 789} end
paren (any text here 321) end

# 11) Strings and escapes (single and double), plus punctuation inside
say "hello world" and "escaped quote \" ok" and "path c:\\tmp\\x"
say 'single quotes' and 'escape \n \t \''

# 12) Reserved words (should be colored unless they are inside a tag)
None is a reserved word here
Todo is a reserved word here
but inside <Todo> it should be a tag name, not a keyword

# 13) Punctuation catch-all (stuff not matched above)
punctuation test: !!! ??? ... ;; :: == != <= >= ~~ ^^^ && || ++ -- // \\

# 14) Words + numbers baseline
words and more_words and mixed123 tokens 42 007 2026

# 15) Single / double / triple backtick fenced blocks (with content)
`single backtick fence content: x y z 123 !@#`

``double backtick fence content: inside here should be todo.fenced.content``

